name: ONE of ONE of ONE | ISSUE 2/4
description:
this is your wallet identifier represented by a series of seemingly random glyphs of a single hue, rising from the void and increasing in luminosity until right before the point of being consumed, representing a continuous exchange of ideas that leads us closer and closer to illumination within a tightly defined scope

have you ever wondered what your special slice of the spectrum is? which of the infinite tones available to us all is the essence of your speciality, and how far along are you on the path to being fully illuminated?

this unique 1/1 goes a step further by adding an additional dimension, ensuring each viewer has their own unique, persistent version of this nft, essentially turning it into a 1/1/1 edition
